        "Title": "Hitman 6. Episode 6. Garden of origins",
        "Location": "LOCATION_ANCESTRAL_SMOOTHSNAKE",
        "PublicId": "133505928120",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Ancestral/scene_smoothsnake.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 428233b2-b247-4fde-aed6-fd8af9b1b537).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning 47. Today you return to Dartmoor, this time for some sort of summer party. The theme of this party is a plant show, and it seems that there have been some uninvited guests. Floyd Moore and his wife Henrietta Shepard. I could swear that those plants in the greenhouses are the same plants used to grow the virus. I don&apos;t want to take any risk. The last target is called Farrell Thorpe, he is dressed as a security guard and is investigating the situation on his phone. Have fun!",
